[size=4][u]Pilot Academy: Ranks and Relations[/u][/size]

This mod introduces the Pilot Academy, allowing the Player to train pilots and improve faction relations through trade operations.

[size=3][u][b]Features[/b][/u][/size]
[list]
[*] [b]Intuitive UI[/b]: Easily manage all Academy operations.
[*] [b]Pilot Training[/b]: Train pilots effectively using trade operations.
[*] [b]Faction Relations[/b]: Improve the Player's standing with other factions through trade.
[*] [b]Wing Organization[/b]: Organize the Player's trainees into Wings for efficient management.
[*] [b]Goal Selection[/b]: Prioritize either pilot training or improving relations.
[*] [b]Faction Limiting[/b]: Restrict training and relation-building activities to specific factions for each Wing.
[*] [b]Researchable Upgrades[/b]:
[list]
[*] Expand to 9 Wings.
[*] Train pilots up to the 5-star rank.
[*] Automatically hire [b]Cadets[/b] from selected factions.
[*] Automatically assign [b]Trained Pilots[/b] to the Player's ships based on priority.
[/list]
[/list]
[size=3][u][b]Limitations[/b][/u][/size]
[list]
[*] The Academy currently only supports small (S-class) ships.
[/list]
